      "title": "When Govt resigns, new govt should be ready \u2013 PM",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lankan Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe in a special statement to the media on Saturday (9) evening that he proposed to the President to establish an All-Party Government.",
        "He said when the existing government resigns, a new Government must be formed and it is not wise for the country go on without a Government."
      ],
